**Dockerfile**

    ENV DEFAULT_JAVA_TOOL_OPTIONS=&quot;-Xmx256m -XX:+HeapDumpOnOutOfMemoryError -XX:HeapDumpPath=/tmp/heapdumps/my-service.hprof -XX:+ExitOnOutOfMemoryError&quot;
    
