    CMD [&quot;/${project.build.finalName}.jar&quot;]

And in the docker-entrypoint.sh we did following:

**docker-entrypoint.sh**

    #!/bin/bash

    JAVA_TOOL_OPTIONS=&quot;$DEFAULT_JAVA_TOOL_OPTIONS $JAVA_TOOL_OPTIONS&quot;
    java -jar &quot;$1&quot;

